<item>
            <title>[LU-4822] Test failure on test suite sanity-scrub, subtest test_9</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4822</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Bob Glossman &amp;lt;bob.glossman@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/50d5956a-b107-11e3-98c2-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/50d5956a-b107-11e3-98c2-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;A search in maloo shows 2 instances of a similar looking failure, both seen on 3/21.  None before, none after.  Seen in testing different patches on different branches.  Suggests some related failure but not due to the different patches under test in these cases.   Unless it starts happening a lot probably not a high priority to fix.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_9 failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;(8) Failed to start OI scrub on mds2&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: sanity-scrub 9&lt;/p&gt;</description>
